<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_rel_widget_clone"><sp_rel_widget_clone action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><child display_value="Copy of Data Table from Instance Definit">e4aa26721bddc21018398485604bcb47</child><cloned>2024-04-05 09:14:58</cloned><last_validated>2024-04-05 09:14:58</last_validated><parent display_value="Data Table from Instance Definition">38058ff1cb11020000f8d856634c9c8c</parent><payload><?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><sp_widget><category>standard</category><client_script><![CDATA[function ($scope, spUtil, $location, spAriaFocusManager) {
	$scope.$on('data_table.click', function(e, parms){
		var p = $scope.data.page_id || 'form';
		var s = {id: p, table: parms.table, sys_id: parms.sys_id, view: 'sp'};
		var newURL = $location.search(s);
		spAriaFocusManager.navigateToLink(newURL.url());
	});
}]]></client_script><controller_as/><css/><data_table>sp_instance_table</data_table><demo_data/><description/><docs/><field_list>table,filter,field_list,maximum_entries,order_by,order_direction,title,color,glyph,sp_page</field_list><has_preview>false</has_preview><id/><internal>false</internal><link/><name>Data Table from Instance Definition</name><option_schema/><public>false</public><roles>snc_external,snc_internal</roles><script><![CDATA[(function(){
	/*  "use strict"; - linter issues */
	// populate the 'data' object
	var sp_page = $sp.getValue('sp_page');
	var pageGR = new GlideRecord('sp_page');
	pageGR.get(sp_page);
	data.page_id = pageGR.getValue("id");
	$sp.getValues(data);
	if (data.field_list) {
		data.fields_array = data.field_list.split(',');
	} else {
		data.field_list = $sp.getListColumns(data.table);
	}

	if (input) {
		data.p = input.p;
		data.o = input.o;
		data.d = input.d;
		data.q = input.q;
	}
	data.p = data.p || 1;
	data.o = data.o || $sp.getValue('order_by');
	data.d = data.d || $sp.getValue('order_direction');

	data.page_index = (data.p - 1);
	data.window_size = $sp.getValue('maximum_entries') || 10;
	data.window_start  = (data.page_index * data.window_size);
	data.window_end = (((data.page_index + 1) * data.window_size));
	data.filter = $sp.getValue("filter");

	var gr = new GlideRecordSecure(data.table);
	if (!gr.isValid()) {
		data.invalid_table = true;
		data.table_label = data.table;
		return;
	}
	data.table_label = gr.getLabel();

	options.table = data.table;
	options.fields = data.field_list;
	options.o=data.o;
	options.d= data.d;
	options.filter=data.filter;
	options.window_size=data.window_size;
	options.view = data.view;
	options.useInstanceTitle = true; // to make sure Data Table widget uses headerTitle always
	options.headerTitle = options.title;
	options.show_breadcrumbs=true;
	
	data.dataTableWidget = $sp.getWidget('widget-data-table', options);
})();]]></script><servicenow>true</servicenow><sys_class_name>sp_widget</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-07-17 21:37:50</sys_created_on><sys_id>38058ff1cb11020000f8d856634c9c8c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>254</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Data Table from Instance Definition</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Service Portal - Core" source="com.glide.service-portal">5fa9083158f0311095d71ac546680122</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_widget_38058ff1cb11020000f8d856634c9c8c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-03-02 12:50:09</sys_updated_on><template><![CDATA[<div>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_7940ef1e1b6c065062f8ea46624bcb7c
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>cmn_schedule_span</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="cmn_schedule_span">u_reserved=false^EQ<item endquery="false" field="u_reserved" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="false"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>AGMD Crear reservas de clases</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    //global.TFM_Horarios.createReservations(current);

    var docenciaModule = "096167f41be5061062f8ea46624bcb31";
    var resModuleGR = new GlideRecord('sn_wsd_rsv_reservable_module');
    resModuleGR.get(docenciaModule);

    var startDateTime = new GlideDateTime(current.getDisplayValue('start_date_time'));
    var startEndDateTime = new GlideDateTime(current.getDisplayValue('end_date_time'));
    var endDateTime = new GlideDateTime(current.getDisplayValue('repeat_until'));

    var diff = GlideDateTime.subtract(startDateTime, endDateTime);
    var days = diff.getDayPart();
    endDateTime = endDateTime.getDate() + " " + startEndDateTime.toString().split(' ')[1];
	endDateTime = new GlideDateTime(endDateTime);
	
	var duration = gs.dateDiff(startDateTime, startEndDateTime, true);
	

    var reservationInput = {
        attendees: current.getValue('u_profesor_responsable'),
        ignore_same_day_validation: false,
        is_private: false,
        location: current.getValue('u_location'),
        number_of_attendees: 1,
        primary_building: current.u_location.building.toString(),
        requested_for: current.getValue('u_profesor_responsable'),
        reservableModuleGr: resModuleGR,
        reservable_module: docenciaModule,
        timezone: "GTM"
    };
    var patternJson = {
        amountOfDates: days,
        duration: duration*1000,
        label: "Repeats weekly",
        options: {
            count: false,
            //count: current.getValue('repeat_count'),
            daysOfWeek: current.getValue('days_of_week'),
            endDate: endDateTime,
            endDateGdt: endDateTime,
            every: 1,
        },
        repeats: current.getValue('repeat_type'),
        startDate: startDateTime,
        startDateGdt: startDateTime,
    };
	
	try {
		var result = new sn_wsd_rsv.WSDRecurringReservationService().createRecurringSeries(reservationInput, patternJson);
	} catch(e) {
		gs.addErrorMessage('Las reservas no han podido ser realizadas, revisa las fechas introducidas');
		return;
	}
    if (result.isValid) {
        gs.addInfoMessage("Reservas realizadas correctamente");
        current.setValue('u_reserved', true);
        current.update();
    } else {
        gs.addErrorMessage(result);
        current.setValue('u_reserved', false);
        current.update();
    }

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>aaron.admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-02-26 17:05:55</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>7940ef1e1b6c065062f8ea46624bcb7c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>58</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AGMD Crear reservas de clases</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_7940ef1e1b6c065062f8ea46624bcb7c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>aaron.admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-05-21 18:52:54</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=7940ef1e1b6c065062f8ea46624bcb7c"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_theme"><sp_theme action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css_variables>      //=New Variables
      //==Text color
      $text-primary:                          #181A1F; //$text-color --now-color_text--primary
      $text-secondary:                        #474D5A; //--now-color_text--secondary
      $text-tertiary:                         #656E81; //$text-muted --now-color_text--tertiary
      $text-white:                            #ffffff; //--now-color--neutral-0

      //==Backgrounds
      $background-primary:                    #ffffff; //--now-color_background--primary
      $background-secondary:                  #f6f6f8; //--now-color_background--secondary
      $background-tertiary:                   #F0F1F5; //--now-color_background--tertiary

      //==borders
      $border-primary:                        #8790A1; //--now-color_border--primary
      $border-secondary:                      #ACB2BE; //--now-color_border--secondary
      $border-tertiary:                       #DADDE2; //--now-color_border--tertiary

      //==colors for selected
      $select-primary: 	                    #007b58; //--now-color_selection--primary-2
      $select-primary-lighter: 	            #D7EBE5; //--now-color_selection--primary-0
      $select-primary-darker: 	            #003929; //--now-color_selection--primary-4

      //==Primary color 
      $brand-primary-darkest:                 #1D1E46; //--now-color--primary-3
      $brand-primary-darker:                  #333579; //--now-color--primary-2
      $brand-primary-lighter:                 #8789D2; //--now-color--interactive-1
      $brand-primary-lightest:                #D1D2EE; //--now-color--primary-0
      $brand-primary-opacity:				 #E3E4F2; //--now-color--primary-0 (with opacity 0.5)

      //==Brand Darker colors
      $brand-danger-darker:                   #CC293C!default; //--now-color_alert--critical-3
      $brand-warning-darker:                  #AFA400!default; //--now-color_alert--warning-3
      $brand-moderate-darker:                 #6B52C4!default; //--now-color_alert--moderate-3 
      $brand-low-darker:                      #6E6F78!default; //--now-color_alert--low-3 
      $brand-success-darker:                  #3B7F00!default; //--now-color_alert--positive-3
      $brand-info-darker:                     #297CB2!default; //--now-color_alert--info-3

      $sp-space--xxs:                         2px;
      $sp-space--xs:     	                    4px;
      $sp-space--sm:     	                    8px;
      $sp-space--md:    	                    12px; 
      $sp-space--lg:     	                    16px;
      $sp-space--xl:		                    24px;
      $sp-space--xxl: 	                    32px;
      $sp-space--3xl: 	                    40px;

      $sp-panel-box-shadow:                   0 4px 8px 0 rgba(23,40,52,0.08);

      //==Subnav background-color
      $sp-nav-subnav:                         $sp-navbar-divider-color;

      //==End new variables ----/


      // Define NavBar
      $sp-navbar-height: 		                60px;
      $sp-navbar-divider-color:               #333579 !default; //--now-color_chrome--divider-10
      $sp-navbar-inverse-bg:                  $navbar-inverse-bg !default;
      $navbar-inverse-bg:                     #181826 !default; //--now-color_chrome--brand-10
      $navbar-inverse-link-color:             #DADDE2 !default; //--now-color--neutral-2
      $navbar-inverse-link-hover-color:       #ffffff !default; //--now-color--neutral-0
      $sp-logo-margin-x: 		                6px !default;
      $sp-logo-margin-y:		                6px !default;
      $sp-tagline-color:		                $text-color !default;

      // Define Body
      $body-bg:								              $background-secondary!default;
      $sp-body-bg:			                    $background-secondary; 
      $table-hover:                         #e6f2ee; //--now-color_surface--brand-1

      $text-color:							            $text-primary!default;
      $text-muted:							            $text-tertiary!default;

      //## Gray and brand colors for use across Bootstrap.
      $gray-base:                             #000000; //--now-color--neutral-21
      $gray-darker:                           #181A1F; //--now-color--neutral-18
      $gray-dark:                             #282C33; //--now-color--neutral-16
      $gray:                                  #4f5664; //--now-color--neutral-11
      $gray-light:                            #656E81; //--now-color--neutral-9
      $gray-lighter:                          #F6F6F8; //--now-color--neutral-1

      $brand-primary:                         #4f52bd!default; //--now-color--primary-1
      $brand-danger:                          #E42338!default; //--now-color_alert--critical-2
      $brand-warning:                         #F0E000!default; //--now-color_alert--warning-2
      $brand-moderate:                        #8B6BFF!default; //--now-color_alert--moderate-2 NEW
      $brand-low:                            	#9698A4!default; //--now-color_alert--low-2 NEW
      $brand-success:                         #51ae00!default; //--now-color_alert--positive-2
      $brand-info:                            #38aaf4!default; //--now-color_alert--info-2

      $primary:                               $brand-primary;
      $warning:                               $brand-warning;
      $success:                               $brand-success;
      $info:                                  $brand-info;
      $danger:                                $brand-danger;
      $error:                                 $danger;

      $color-darkest:                         #181A1F; //--now-color--neutral-18
      $color-darker: 	                        #474D5A; //--now-color--neutral-12
      $color-dark:                            #575F6E; //--now-color--neutral-10
      $color-disabled:                        #9AA1AF; //--now-color--neutral-6
      $color-light:                           #BDC2CB; //--now-color--neutral-4
      $color-lighter:                         #F0F1F5; //--now-color--neutral-2
      $color-lightest:                        #ffffff; //--now-color--neutral-0
      $color-accent:                          #007b58; //--now-color_selection--primary-2
      $color-accent-light:                    #51A58D; //--now-color_selection--primary-1
      $color-accent-lightest:                 #D7EBE5; //--now-color_selection--primary-0

      $border:                                $border-tertiary;
      $panel-primary:                         $border;

      $overdue:                               $brand-danger;
      $due-today:                             $brand-warning;
      $due-later:                             $brand-success;
      $complete:                              $brand-low;
      $in-progress:                           $brand-success;

      $color-blue-lightest:                   #D9F4F9; //--now-color_grouped--blue-0
      $color-blue-light:                      #A0E3EF; //--now-color_grouped--blue-1
      $color-blue-dark:                       #3A7782; //--now-color_grouped--blue-4
      $color-grey:                            #C6CBCB; //--now-color_grouped--gray-1
      $color-green-dark:                      #1C4122; //--now-color_grouped--green-5

      $progress-bar:                          $brand-primary;

      //define service portal preview outline highlighting
      $preview-outline:                       #1A4E70; //--now-color_alert--info-4
      $preview-outline-text-color:            #ffffff; //--now-color--neutral-0



      ////Bootstrap variable

      //** Global textual link color.
      $link-color:                            #3c59e7; //--now-color--link-2
      $link-hover-color:                      #263994; //--now-color--link-3

      //== Typography
      $font-family-sans-serif:                "Lato", sans-serif;

      $font-size-base:                        16px; 
      $font-size-3xl:                         ceil(($font-size-base * 2.25)); // 36px New
      $font-size-xxl:                         ceil(($font-size-base * 1.875)); // 30px  New
      $font-size-xl:                          ceil(($font-size-base * 1.5)); // 24px New
      $font-size-large:                       ceil(($font-size-base * 1.25)); // 20px  
      $font-size-md:                          $font-size-base;  // 16px New
      $font-size-small:                       ceil(($font-size-base * 0.875)); // 14px
      $font-size-xs:                          ceil(($font-size-base * 0.75)); // 12px New 

      $font-size-h1:                          ceil(($font-size-base * 2)); // 32px 
      $font-size-h2:                          ceil(($font-size-base * 1.5)); // 24px 
      $font-size-h3:                          ceil(($font-size-base * 1.25)); // 20px 
      $font-size-h4:                          ceil(($font-size-base * 1.125)); // 18px 
      $font-size-h5:                          $font-size-base; 
      $font-size-h6:                          ceil(($font-size-base * 0.875)); // 14px  

      $line-height-base:                      1.4;

      $headings-font-family:                  'Lato', sans-serif;
      $headings-font-weight:                  600;
      $headings-line-height:                  1.1;

      //== Components
      //
      $padding-base-vertical:                 6px;
      $padding-base-horizontal:               $sp-space--lg;

      $padding-large-vertical:                $sp-space--sm;
      $padding-large-horizontal:              $sp-space--xl;

      $padding-small-vertical:                $sp-space--xs;
      $padding-small-horizontal:              $sp-space--md;

    var endDate = current.getDisplayValue('end_date_time');
    var repeatTime = current.getDisplayValue('repeat_until');

    if (!gs.nil(repeatTime)) {

        var endDateGdt = new GlideDateTime(endDate);
        var repeatTimeGdt = new GlideDateTime(repeatTime);

        if (repeatTimeGdt < endDateGdt) {
            gs.addErrorMessage('Repeat until time cannot be before the end time');
            current.setAbortAction(true);
            return;
        }

    }

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>aaron.admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-03-08 14:07:54</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>9201a7751bb0461062f8ea46624bcb36</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AGMD Prevenir horario fin antes inicio</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_9201a7751bb0461062f8ea46624bcb36</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>aaron.admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-05-21 18:54:23</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=9201a7751bb0461062f8ea46624bcb36"/></record_update>
